          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Wilkesbarre</placeName>
                                        <date>Aug 24<hi rend="sup">th</hi>
                                                  <hi rend="underline">5609</hi></date>.</p>
                              <p><addressee>Rev Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Yours Respectfully is at<lb/> hand, <persName>Mr
                                                  Long</persName>, request me to state to you<lb/>
                                        that the <sic>Synagoge</sic> will be <sic>consicrated</sic>
                                        by<lb/> the <persName>Rev. Mr. Isaacs</persName> of
                                                  <placeName>New York</placeName>.</p>
                              <p>We would be happy to have you here also on<lb/> the
                                                  <sic>ocasion</sic>, as for the part you should
                                        take<lb/> we <sic>ar</sic> not able to say, if you come, you
                                        have<lb/> to <sic>arange</sic> that with <persName>Mr
                                                  Isaacs</persName>.</p>
                              <p>The Books you mentioned in your Letter, have<lb/> not
                                                  <sic>arived</sic>, it is likely <persName>Mr
                                                  Hakenburg</persName>
                                        <sic>hase</sic><lb/>
                                        <sic>vergotten</sic> to forward them, I will my <add>?</add>
                                        and sell<lb/> what I can, and <sic>remitt</sic> you the
                                        Money.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully &amp; Obt</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)">
                                        <persName role="author">M. W. Strously</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>P. S.</p>
                              <p>We respect <persName>Mr.<lb/>Isaacs</persName> early next week</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev. Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>371 Walnut Str</placeName>:</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">
                                        <placeName>
                                                  <hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi>
                                        </placeName>
                              </p>
